# Syntax aside

## Pipes

-   2014+ magrittr pipe `%>%`

-   2021+ (R $\geq$ 4.1.0) native R pipe `|>`

2022 Isabella VelÃ¡squez Understanding the native R pipe \|\> <https://ivelasq.rbind.io/blog/understanding-the-r-pipe/>

