## Plan the variables you want to collect

<br>

:::: {.columns}

::: {.column width="50%"}

**Necessary to plan for**

- Variable name
- Variable label/item wording
- Variable type
- Allowable values/ranges
- Missing values

:::

::: {.column width="50%"}

**Nice to plan for**

- Skip patterns
- Required items
- Variable universe

:::

