### Solution

::: {.cell hash='index_cache/revealjs/unnamed-chunk-31_ef561f9e4c79ddc398e2cc1fd4c512c5'}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="3"}
df_clean <- df_raw |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  janitor::remove_empty(which = c("rows", "cols"))
